<item>
            <title>[PIG-411] Pig leaves HOD processes behind if Ctrl-C is used before HOD connection is fully established</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-411</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The code in doHod in backend/hadoop/executionengine/HExecutionEngine.java waits for hod connection to be fully established before setting a flag that indicates need to discunnect. The flag should be set as soon as HOD process is created so that we destroy it. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This change will not guarantee that process is not left behind but would make it much less likely&lt;/p&gt;</description>
